document.full_text: in talks with south africa president jacob zuma, the libya leader col. muammar el-qaddafi 'emphasized' that he will not leave libya despite air attacks and international pressure.
document.title: zuma's office says qaddafi intent on staying in libya
lines_and_colors: in talks with south africa president jacob zuma, the libya leader col. muammar el-qaddafi 'emphasized' that he will not leave libya despite air attacks and international pressure.
